    com.bt.graphml.group  

    • Uses of GroupMaker in com.bt.graphml.group

      Classes in com.bt.graphml.group that implement GroupMaker 
      Modifier and Type Class and Description
      class  GroupBySize
      group the elements by size. elements that are the only one of their size are left alone.
      class  GroupRandomly
      randomly group the given elements
      class  NestedGroupBySize
      recursivly groups elements by size following this behaviour: elements that have a extent smaller than mid = min + (max - min) / 2 (min and max being the minimum and maximum sizes) are added to one group, the others to another one.
      class  NoGrouping
